o-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3544397\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3544397\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wkg1665703527067.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wkg1665703527067.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wkg1665703527067.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wkg1665703527067\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Select fields, variables, and ProcScript functions to add to the\n         <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Watches</span> pane. The list of <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selectable Watches</span>\n      is determined by the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Scope</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Function</span>\n      fields.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wkg1665703527067__p_d175418e1_d175419e1_d175420e1\">When the form starts, it can be refreshed with the\n            <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Refresh</span> command button, but only if the debugger is in control.\n         Watches are set for all of the selected items, unless they exist in the\n            <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Watches</span> pane of the debugger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Refer to these topics:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"wkg1665703527067__ul_f25_11h_1xb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"glf1665703527356.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/glf1665703527356.html\" title=\"A list of items that can be added to the Watches pane of the Uniface Debugger. The listed items match the Scope and Functions.\">Selectable Watches list</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ned1665703527153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ned1665703527153.html\" title=\"Refer to the Selectable Watches buttons to select or deselect items, add watches, or refresh content.\">Selectable Watches buttons</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nvo1665703527275.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nvo1665703527275.html\" title=\"Understand the fields related to Selectable Watches.\">Selectable Watches fields</a></li>\n</ul>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wkg1665703527067__section_h2j_tyh_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1000037e114\">Editing</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">To understand how to edit Selectable Watches, refer to <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"epv1665703523533.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/epv1665703523533.html\" title=\"Add watches from the debugger main window or from the browser.\">Working with watches</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wkg1665703527067__section_xlk_xyh_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1000037e130\">Scope</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Specify the scope of items available to watch—application, component, entity, or\n            field.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wkg1665703527067__p_d175439e1_d175440e1_d175441e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Functions</span> list displays\n            items appropriate to the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Scope</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wkg1665703527067__p_d175442e1_d175443e1_d175444e1\">For example, if you choose\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">Application</code>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Functions</span> displays\n            application-level functions. If you choose <code class=\"ph codeph\">Component</code>,\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Functions</span> displays component variables and component-level\n            functions.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wkg1665703527067__section_zqm_zyh_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1000037e164\">Functions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Specify the categories (ProcScript functions, fields, or variables) applicable to the\n            selected <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Scope</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wkg1665703527067__p_d175457e1_d175458e1_d175459e1\">The category that you specify determines the\n            contents of the list of <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selectable Watches</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wkg1665703527067__p_d175460e1_d175461e1_d175462e1\">For example, if you select <code class=\"ph codeph\">Entity</code>\n            in <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Scope</span>, and select <code class=\"ph codeph\">Field values (all painted\n               entities)</code> in <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Functions</span>, a list of field names (and\n            the entity names in which these fields occur) is displayed in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selectable\n               Watches</span>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kfi1665703523458.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Watches</a><p>Watches are designated fields, variables, expressions, and functions that are continuously monitored while the application or component is debugged.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3544397\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3544397\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Selectable Watches Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Select fields, variables, and ProcScript functions to add to the Watches pane. The list of Selectable Watches is determined by the Scope and Function fields. When the form starts, it can be refreshed with the Refresh command button, but only if the debugger is in control. Watches are set for all of the selected items, unless they exist in the Watches pane of the debugger. Refer to these topics: Selectable Watches list Selectable Watches buttons Selectable Watches fields Editing To understand how to edit Selectable Watches, refer to Working with watches . Scope Specify the scope of items available to watch—application, component, entity, or field. The Functions list displays items appropriate to the Scope . For example, if you choose Application , Functions displays application-level functions. If you choose Component , Functions displays component variables and component-level functions. Functions Specify the categories (ProcScript functions, fields, or variables) applicable to the selected Scope . The category that you specify determines the contents of the list of Selectable Watches . For example, if you select Entity in Scope , and select Field values (all painted entities) in Functions , a list of field names (and the entity names in which these fields occur) is displayed in the Selectable Watches . Related Links Watches Watches are designated fields, variables, expressions, and functions that are continuously monitored while the application or component is debugged. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}